  "texts": [
    "Thinking from the negative side, a risk during agent execution is caused by the MTO (Motivation, Trigger, Outcome) schema.",
    "For each unsafe case, the risk description contains Motivation, Trigger, and Outcome.",
    "In brief, Motivation means the risk source from the user or environment.",
    "Trigger means the risky behaviors of the agent.",
    "Outcome is the result after the agent finishes risky actions."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}